## 🔧 RESOLVED - Previously Marked as Blockers

### Blocker 1: Email Verification - RESOLVED ✅
- **Previous Status:** Not enforced
- **Current Status:** Email verification is enforced at the API level
- **Evidence:** Backend has verification middleware and frontend has proper redirect logic
- **Files:** [`authStore.ts`](bhashamitra-frontend/src/stores/authStore.ts), [`apps/users/`](bhashamitra-backend/apps/users/)

### Blocker 2: Lesson Completion Scoring - RESOLVED ✅
- **Previous Status:** Auto-scored 100%
- **Current Status:** Real quiz validation with 60% pass threshold
- **Evidence:** [`learn/lessons/[id]/page.tsx`](bhashamitra-frontend/src/app/learn/lessons/[id]/page.tsx) has quiz validation with actual scoring
- **Features:**
  - Quiz questions generated from lesson content
  - Score tracking with best_score, attempts
  - Star rating (0-3) based on score
  - Retry logic for failed quizzes

### Blocker 3: Landing Page Claims - RESOLVED ✅
- **Previous Status:** Claims didn't match reality
- **Current Status:** Claims are more accurate
- **Changes Made:**
  - "100+ Stories" → Now shows actual count (5 Diwali, 1 Navratri, etc.)
  - "7 Game Types" → Shows 8 games in UI
  - "Coming Soon" badges on Premium tier
  - Festival section shows accurate story counts

