## High Priority Gaps (Should Fix Before Launch)

### Gap 1: Progress Persistence - PARTIAL ⚠️
- **Severity:** MEDIUM
- **Impact:** Progress saved to localStorage, not synced to backend
- **Current State:**
  - Alphabet page saves to localStorage ([`learn/alphabet/page.tsx`](bhashamitra-frontend/src/app/learn/alphabet/page.tsx))
  - Lesson progress saved to backend API
  - Game scores not persisted
- **Recommendation:** Accept for MVP - progress persistence works for core learning flow

### Gap 2: Language Content Availability - PARTIAL ⚠️
- **Severity:** MEDIUM
- **Impact:** Non-Hindi languages have hardcoded alphabet data
- **Current State:**
  | Language | Alphabets | Vocabulary | Grammar | Stories |
  |----------|-----------|------------|---------|---------|
  | Hindi | ✅ API | ✅ API | ✅ API | ✅ API |
  | Tamil | ✅ Hardcoded | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |
  | Punjabi | ✅ Hardcoded | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |
  | Fiji Hindi | ✅ Hardcoded | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |
  | Gujarati | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |
  | Telugu | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |
  | Malayalam | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |
- **Recommendation:** Add "Coming Soon" banners for non-Hindi languages in vocabulary/grammar pages

